{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place butter in mixing bowl and melt <b>2 min 30 sec\/80°C\/speed 2<b>. Brush insides of a 12 hole madeleine tray with melted butter then dust each hole with a little flour and tap out any excess. Place in fridge to chill until needed. Transfer remaining butter to a small bowl and set aside."," <strong>Insert butterfly whisk<\/strong>. Place caster sugar, eggs, lemon zest and juice of 1 lemon in mixing bowl then whisk <b>5 min\/37°C\/speed 3<b>.","Add flour, baking powder and reserved melted butter then mix <b>10 sec\/speed 2<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula then mix again <b>5 sec\/speed 2<b>. Cover mixing bowl with cling film and place in fridge to chill for 4 hours.","Towards the end of this time, preheat oven to 180°C and place a sheet of baking paper under a wire rack.","Place mixing bowl back into position and re-mix rested batter <b>5 sec\/speed 2<b>. <strong>Remove butterfly whisk<\/strong>. Fill holes of cold madeleine tray ⅔ full. Bake for 10 minutes (180°C) or until well-risen and golden. Leave to cool in tray for 2 minutes then transfer madeleines to prepared wire rack.","In a small bowl, mix together granulated sugar and juice of remaining 2 lemons until just combined. Prick madeleines all over with a cocktail stick then carefully spoon over lemon mixture. Leave to cool completely before serving."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["100 g unsalted butter, diced","100 g caster sugar","2 large eggs","3 lemons, finely grated zest of 1 and freshly squeezed juice of 3","100 g plain flour, plus extra for dusting","¾ tsp baking powder","3 Tbsp granulated sugar"]}],"id":"r364979","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-Kw1mwzCxnFk\/XZWq8-ptAAI\/AAAAAAAAff0\/yMtpTUB6U44XWKN6qTWlHq3qSpo9XgjFgCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_ZIkmAam5rTnyteOl.png","title":"Lemon Drizzle Madeleines","publishedAt":"2018-08-13T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"2 g","fat":"6 g","uom":"per 1 piece","carbohydrates":"15 g","calories":"505 kJ \/ 120 kcal"},"usefulItems":"wire rack, baking paper, cling film, pastry brush, cocktail stick, 12 hole madeleine tray, refrigerator, oven","basicInfo":["easy","30m","4h 45m","12 pieces"]}